          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A He-4 gas cell with a 8-mm diameter nickel window of",
                " 0.5 to 1-mum thickness. The gas cell is insulated from",
                "the beam line and the entire chamber, including a",
                "Cu-catcher of 50-mm diameter that is in electric",
                "contact with the gas cell, serves as a Faraday cup.",
                "The He-4 purity of 99.9% was ensured by replacing it",
                "periodically every four hours."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. The number of beam particles obtained",
                "through either the beam current integration or the",
                " Rutherford scattering from the nickel foil is the",
                "major source of error in the determination of the cross",
                "section.",
                "Reaction (13-AL-27(P,G)14-SI-28) has been used for beam",
                "energy calibration."
              ]
            }
          ],
